[?2004l[?2004h>     "roles": ["admin", "editor"]  # Array of roles assigned to the user (may be empty)
[?2004l[?2004h>   },
[?2004l[?2004h>   ...
[?2004l[?2004h> ]
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **Output Data Schema**:
[?2004l[?2004h> The output JSON file '"'"'/app/active_users_report.json'"'"' must be an array of objects with the following structure:
[?2004l[?2004h> [
[?2004l[?2004h>   {
[?2004l[?2004h>     "user_id": 1,                 # Derived from '"'"'id'"'"' in input 
