[?2004l[?2004h>   },
[?2004l[?2004h>   ...
[?2004l[?2004h> ]
[?2004l[?2004h> 
[?2004l[?2004h> **Requirements**:
[?2004l[?2004h> - You must use jq to perform this transformation. Using other programming languages (e.g., Python, Ruby) is strictly prohibited.
